    +paragraph("Who should I contact if I have questions or comments?")
        | You may contact us with any question or comment at 
        a(href="mailto: uofg.virtualagents@gmail.com", title="uofg.virtualagents@gmail.com") uofg.virtualagents@gmail.com

    +paragraph("Should I participate?")
        | You are invited to take part in a scientific research study. It is important for you to understand why the research is being conducted and what participating in the study involves. Please take your time to familiarise yourself with this information.

    +paragraph("What is the purpose of the study?")
        | This study is interested in evaluating a recipe recommender system.

    +paragraph("Do I have to take part?")
        | Your participation in this study is completely voluntary and you may withdraw at any time without any specific reason as well as without any repercussions.

    +paragraph("What will the study involve if I take part?")
        //- | The study consists of three parts. In the first part, you will have to answer some questionnaires about yourself and about your food preferences. 
