        //- you will have to rate some recipes according to your personal preferences.
        | In the second part,
        | you will will be presented with two lists of recipes and will have to choose a few you like.
        | In the second part, you will have to fill in two questionnaires: the first one about what is important to you when you look for a recipe, the second one about demographics.
        | Should you wish to withdraw from the study this is possible at any point without any further repercussions. The study should take no more than 15 minutes.

    +paragraph("Will my taking part in this study be kept confidential?")
        | All the data collected in this study will be kept in strict confidentiality. 
        | The information provided by you will be used only in research and will not be tied to any identifiable information. 
        | The data will be stored in a password-protected file at the University of Glasgow, 
        | will be archived and may be uploaded to digital data repositories such as the Open Science Framework in an anonymised form, 
        | according to current data sharing practices.

    +paragraph("What will happen to the results of this study?")
        | The results of this study will be analysed and interpreted by the principal investigator for a research project at the University of Glasgow 
